          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Spectroscopically pure Zn metal, disc 16.6 g/cm2"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The observed behaviour of the cross section at wave-",
                "lengths 3.37, 4.18, 4.62 and 4.95 Angstrom correspond",
                "to Bragg edges due to reflections from the planes",
                " (102), (101), (100) and (002) respectively, of the",
                "hexagonal crystal structure of the sample which is",
                "confirmed by x-ray diffraction analysis.",
                "At energies between 0.05 eV and 0.4 eV the expression",
                "obtained for the cross section is",
                "sigma tot = (3.79+-0.12) + (0.13+-0.03)*Sqrt(E)   barns",
                "which gives  sigma tot (0.025 eV) = 4.61+-0.31 barns"
              ]
            }
          ],
